Focus on user, needs, problems then solutions. 
Do it fast in Plan, Do, Check, Act. 

Diffrent Risks, not only for the whole product, also for each feature. 

Desirability Risk (Will es jemand?)
	User Interviews (ohne direkte fragen, sondern ob das problem besteht, und wie es gelöst wird) 	Landing Page Test
	Pre-Order / Crowdfunding

Feasibility Risk (Kann ich es bauen?) 	Technical Spike
	Proof of Concept
	API Mocking

Viability Risk (Lohnt es sich wirtschaftlich?)
	Pricing Test (A/B)
	fake door, Smoke Test mit Preisschild
	Research, Business Model Canvas

Usability Risk (Kann es die Zielgruppe bedienen?)
	Prototyp:, lovable, bolt.new
	Paper Prototyping
	Automation 
